  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides arguments for cloning a <see cref="SkiaSharp.SKTypeface" /> with custom variation and palette settings.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontArguments` is a `ref struct` that collects the parameters used when calling <xref:SkiaSharp.SKTypeface.Clone*> to create a modified copy of a typeface. It supports setting a variation design position, a font collection index, a color palette index, and per-entry palette color overrides.

## Examples

```csharp
var args = new SKFontArguments
{
    CollectionIndex = 0,
    PaletteIndex = 1
};
using var cloned = typeface.Clone(args);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
